# Scheduling & receivers

- Primary scheduling lives in `BackupJobs` + `SmsJobService` (+ `AlarmManagerDriver` fallback). Migration target is **WorkManager**, not more JobDispatcher.
- Runtime registration for SMS/MMS/`com.zegoggles.smssync.BACKUP` is intentional (Android 8+); see `App.onCreate()` / `registerReceiver` with `RECEIVER_EXPORTED` on API 26+.
- Prefer matching existing Java style (package `com.zegoggles.smssync`, Otto bus, preference keys in `Preferences`).
- When touching manifests, keep `android:exported` explicit on components with intent filters.
- Do not remove RCS/group addressing logic in mail conversion without review.
